  BODYWEIGHT
  STRENGTH
  POWERLIFTING
  CALISTHENIC
  PLYOMETRICS
  STRETCHING
  STRONGMAN
  CARDIO
  STABILIZATION
  POWER
  RESISTANCE
  CROSSFIT
  WEIGHTLIFTING
  BICEPS
  SHOULDERS
  CHEST
  BACK
  GLUTES
  TRICEPS
  HAMSTRINGS
  QUADRICEPS
  FOREARMS
  CALVES
  TRAPS
  ABDOMINALS
  NECK
  LATS
  ADDUCTORS
  ABDUCTORS
  OBLIQUES
  GROIN
  FULL_BODY
  ROTATOR_CUFF
  HIP_FLEXOR
  ACHILLES_TENDON
  FINGERS
  DUMBBELL
  KETTLEBELLS
  BARBELL
  SMITH_MACHINE
  BODY_ONLY
  OTHER
  BANDS
  EZ_BAR
  MACHINE
  DESK
  PULLUP_BAR
  NONE
  CABLE
  MEDICINE_BALL
  SWISS_BALL
  FOAM_ROLL
  WEIGHT_PLATE
  TRX
